---
title: Chermoula Pork Bowl with Carrot Couscous & Tomato Salad
description: This meal is all about the little differences – the chermoula spicing up the pork, the flavourful couscous flecked with carrot and the yoghurt drizzle with a mint garnish that will become your new favourite accompaniment.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-pork-bowl-edbf39f2.jpg
